:{"link":"https://www.themoviedb.org/movie/1002161-transamazonia/watch?locale=IT","flatrate":[{"logo_path":"/iZzlUo191ynXNpPNdcY8vvlYSf6.jpg","provider_id":1728,"provider_name":"iWonder Full Amazon channel","display_priority":44}]}}},"wikidata_id":"Q127386034","tvdb_id":null,"wikipedia_url":null,"overview_source":"tmdb","import_batch_id":null,"import_batch_name":null,"imported_at":"2026-02-07T14:49:53.785279+00:00","region":"CN","main_poster":"/zHV02lJqwmYMqxZeezaQk1mwCTL.jpg","images":{"logos":[],"posters":[{"width":720,"height":1080,"file_path":"/zHV02lJqwmYMqxZeezaQk1mwCTL.jpg","iso_639_1":"en","vote_average":3.334},{"width":1666,"height":2500,"file_path":"/waNhJrovhFmsGES35KEHLfCoqtW.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"vote_average":0.166},{"width":1170,"height":1754,"file_path":"/7F8wWaZHMi8hdyejUZwBrZxxY2V.jpg","iso_639_1":"de","vote_average":0},{"width":810,"height":1080,"file_path":"/nHrKUtPS4laKhNsZ3s0egX9OWHu.jpg","iso_639_1":"fr","vote_average":0},{"width":532,"height":750,"file_path":"/1J4oERRGtuYAQmIGi1Mv7yJ57ne.jpg","iso_639_1":"zh","vote_average":0},{"width":1125,"height":1688,"file_path":"/pGgNLv1NbSW1xYpDU1ILJNxGUPT.jpg","iso_639_1":"pt","vote_average":0}],"backdrops":[{"width":3840,"height":2160,"file_path":"/cnHo0cS5Y5cMGmMIS3wQmwZqRvs.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"vote_average":3.334},{"width":3840,"height":2160,"file_path":"/hnSYGOKBJeDz2JOPfdNq7zOfjJt.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"vote_average":0.166},{"width":3200,"height":1800,"file_path":"/2AKTl9tA75EpB4H77fy3qJSf5ND.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"vote_average":0},{"width":3200,"height":1800,"file_path":"/VGjjG7YfT5q1g4LlB2h0kW7miZ.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"vote_average":0},{"width":3200,"height":1800,"file_path":"/ymZ6Qmo28JlLcnGrBgX8ny8L2h3.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"vote_average":0},{"width":3200,"height":1800,"file_path":"/aPZMQ0BuiYAnmL0ryy0J4SMuXx2.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"vote_average":0}]},"enriched_at":"2026-04-21T05:05:33.326+00:00","enrichment_cycle":1,"translations":[{"data":{"title":"","runtime":100,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Rebecca est une jeune guérisseuse miraculeuse, dont la renommée attire les foules vers la mission de son père Lawrence Byrne, au plus profond de la forêt amazonienne. Alors que l'hostilité surgit entre la tribu indigène voisine et les bûcherons illégaux qui envahissent leur territoire, Rebecca et Byrne sont entraînés dans un conflit qui s'intensifie. Les événements plongent Rebecca dans le mystère de son propre passé. Alors que le doute s'insinue dans leur relation, père et fille réalisent qu'ils ne peuvent pas prêcher la paix sans affronter leurs propres démons."},"name":"Français","iso_639_1":"fr","iso_3166_1":"FR","english_name":"French"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":112,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Rebecca, the daughter of missionary Lawrence Byrne, was declared a “miracle” after she survived a plane crash as a child, deep in the Amazon Forest. Years later, Rebecca, who became a famous healer in the region, and her father find themselves embroiled in an escalating conflict when illegal loggers invade the land belonging to the indigenous people they are evangelizing."},"name":"English","iso_639_1":"en","iso_3166_1":"US","english_name":"English"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":112,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Rebecca (Helena Zengel), córka misjonarza, została uznana za „cud” po tym, jak przeżyła katastrofę samolotu jako dziecko, głęboko w amazońskiej dżungli. Lata później stała się cudotwórczynią, podtrzymując ich misję dzięki swojej sławie. Ale kiedy nielegalni drwale wkraczają na tereny należące do rdzennych mieszkańców, których ewangelizują, jej ojciec manewruje nimi w epicentrum tego eskalującego konfliktu."},"name":"Polski","iso_639_1":"pl","iso_3166_1":"PL","english_name":"Polish"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":112,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Rebecca, die Tochter des Missionars Lawrence Byrne, wurde als „Wunder“ bezeichnet, nachdem sie als Kind tief im Amazonas-Regenwald einen Flugzeugabsturz überlebt hatte. Jahre später geraten Rebecca, die in der Region zu einer berühmten Heilerin wurde, und ihr Vater in einen eskalierenden Konflikt, als illegale Holzfäller in das Land der Ureinwohner eindringen, die sie missionieren wollen."},"name":"Deutsch","iso_639_1":"de","iso_3166_1":"DE","english_name":"German"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":""},"name":"Português","iso_639_1":"pt","iso_3166_1":"PT","english_name":"Portuguese"},{"data":{"title":"亞馬遜迷走","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"一架飛機失事迫降在亞馬遜叢林深處，機上人員全數罹難，唯獨小女孩生還。她的人生自此頂著「奇蹟女孩」的聖名，卻只能將遇難的痛楚塵封進回憶，成為治癒他人的靈性治療者，也成為維繫傳教士父親與當地原住民關係的協調者。然而，雨林豐富的天然資源吸引盜伐者前來，各群體間的血腥衝突一觸即發，同為外來者的她與父親，該如何在不同陣營之間取得一席之地？而不願談及的過往，也終將浮上檯面。"},"name":"普通话","iso_639_1":"zh","iso_3166_1":"TW","english_name":"Mandarin"},{"data":{"title":"穿越亚马逊","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"丽贝卡是一位艺术高超的年轻治疗师，她的名声吸引了大批人群来到她父亲劳伦斯·伯恩位于亚马逊雨林深处的传教所。随着邻近原住民部落与非法侵入他们领地的伐木者之间矛盾的升级，丽贝卡和她的父亲被卷入了一场不断升级的冲突中。一连串的事件让丽贝卡开始回想自己的过去。当怀疑开始侵蚀丽贝卡和她父亲之间的关系时，父女俩意识到，如果不面对自己的心魔，他们是无法宣扬和平的。"},"name":"普通话","iso_639_1":"zh","iso_3166_1":"CN","english_name":"Mandarin"},{"data":{"title":"Transamazônia","runtime":112,"tagline":"","homepage":"https://filmesdoestacao.com.br/transamazonia/","overview":"Rebecca, filha do missionário Lawrence Byrne, foi declarada um milagre por ter sobrevivido a um acidente de avião na Floresta Amazônica quando criança. Anos depois, ela se torna uma curandeira milagrosa, sustentando a missão com sua fama crescente. Quando madeireiros ilegais invadem as terras dos povos indígenas que estão sendo evangelizados, o pai de Rebecca coloca a família no epicentro de um conflito que só tende a piorar."},"name":"Português","iso_639_1":"pt","iso_3166_1":"BR","english_name":"Portuguese"}],"reviews_tmdb":[{"id":"671568c39943637ce58270db","url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/review/671568c39943637ce58270db","author":"Brent Marchant","content":"$11","created_at":"2024-10-20T20:32:03.362Z","updated_at":"2024-10-20T20:32:03.434Z","author_details":{"name":"Brent Marchant","rating":8,"username":"Brent_Marchant","avatar_path":null}}],"recommendations":[{"id":1153714,"adult":false,"title":"Death of a Unicorn","video":false,"overview":"A father and daughter accidentally hit and kill a unicorn while en route to a weekend retreat, where his billionaire boss seeks to exploit the creature’s miraculous curative properties.","genre_ids":[27,14,35],"media_type":"movie","popularity":6.826,"vote_count":739,"poster_path":"/xWlF2i51zUq7BUq4iJte1g9NyIM.jpg","release_date":"2025-03-27","vote_average":6.394,"backdrop_path":"/4rLaMBcCJ1pMq72vCulBMPsbAyh.jpg","original_title":"Death of a Unicorn","original_language":"en"},{"id":597,"adult":false,"title":"Titanic","video":false,"overview":"101-year-old Rose DeWitt Bukater tells the story of her life aboard the Titanic, 84 years later. A young Rose boards the ship with her mother and fiancé. Meanwhile, Jack Dawson and Fabrizio De Rossi win third-class tickets aboard the ship. Rose tells the whole story from Titanic's departure through to its death—on its first and last voyage—on April 15, 1912.","genre_ids":[18,10749],"media_type":"movie","popularity":29.365,"vote_count":26817,"poster_path":"/9xjZS2rlVxm8SFx8kPC3aIGCOYQ.jpg","release_date":"1997-12-18","vote_average":7.902,"backdrop_path":"/xnHVX37XZEp33hhCbYlQFq7ux1J.jpg","original_title":"Titanic","original_language":"en"},{"id":872585,"adult":false,"title":"Oppenheimer","video":false,"overview":"The story of J. Robert Oppenheimer's role in the development of the atomic bomb during World War II.","genre_ids":[18,36],"media_type":"movie","popularity":22.369,"vote_count":11379,"poster_path":"/8Gxv8gSFCU0XGDykEGv7zR1n2ua.jpg","release_date":"2023-07-19","vote_average":8.034,"backdrop_path":"/ycnO0cjsAROSGJKuMODgRtWsHQw.jpg","original_title":"Oppenheimer","original_language":"en"},{"id":475557,"adult":false,"title":"Joker","video":false,"overview":"During the 1980s, a failed stand-up comedian is driven insane and turns to a life of crime and chaos in Gotham City while becoming an infamous psychopathic crime figure.","genre_ids":[80,53,18],"media_type":"movie","popularity":20.2141,"vote_count":27332,"poster_path":"/udDclJoHjfjb8Ekgsd4FDteOkCU.jpg","release_date":"2019-10-01","vote_average":8.128,"backdrop_path":"/hO7KbdvGOtDdeg0W4Y5nKEHeDDh.jpg","original_title":"Joker","original_language":"en"},{"id":264660,"adult":false,"title":"Ex Machina","video":false,"overview":"Caleb, a coder at the world's largest internet company, wins a competition to spend a week at a private mountain retreat belonging to Nathan, the reclusive CEO of the company. But when Caleb arrives at the remote location he finds that he will have to participate in a strange and fascinating experiment in which he must interact with the world's first true artificial intelligence, housed in the body of a beautiful robot girl.","genre_ids":[18,878],"media_type":"movie","popularity":8.5844,"vote_count":14038,"poster_path":"/dmJW8IAKHKxFNiUnoDR7JfsK7Rp.jpg","release_date":"2015-01-21","vote_average":7.573,"backdrop_path":"/uqOuJ50EtTj7kkDIXP8LCg7G45D.jpg","original_title":"Ex Machina","original_language":"en"},{"id":150540,"adult":false,"title":"Inside Out","video":false,"overview":"When 11-year-old Riley moves to a new city, her Emotions team up to help her through the transition. Joy, Fear, Anger, Disgust and Sadness work together, but when Joy and Sadness get lost, they must journey through unfamiliar places to get back home.","genre_ids":[16,10751,12,18,35],"media_type":"movie","popularity":15.6045,"vote_count":23182,"poster_path":"/2H1TmgdfNtsKlU9jKdeNyYL5y8T.jpg","release_date":"2015-06-17","vote_average":7.909,"backdrop_path":"/jJKZaTBNenlFclQyjrnvzkRmvWE.jpg","original_title":"Inside Out","original_language":"en"},{"id":37165,"adult":false,"title":"The Truman Show","video":false,"overview":"An insurance salesman begins to suspect that his whole life is actually some sort of reality TV show.","genre_ids