"},{"id":10681,"adult":false,"title":"WALL·E","video":false,"overview":"After hundreds of years doing what he was built for, WALL•E— a robot designed to clean up the earth—discovers a new purpose in life when he meets a sleek search robot named EVE. EVE comes to realize that WALL•E has inadvertently stumbled upon the key to the planet's future, and races back to space to report to the humans. Meanwhile, WALL•E chases EVE across the galaxy and sets into motion one of the most imaginative adventures ever brought to the big screen.","genre_ids":[16,10751,878],"media_type":"movie","popularity":14.5561,"vote_count":19943,"poster_path":"/hbhFnRzzg6ZDmm8YAmxBnQpQIPh.jpg","release_date":"2008-06-22","vote_average":8.107,"backdrop_path":"/fK5ssgvtI43z19FoWigdlqgpLRE.jpg","original_title":"WALL·E","original_language":"en"},{"id":495764,"adult":false,"title":"Birds of Prey (and the Fantabulous Emancipation of One Harley Quinn)","video":false,"overview":"Harley Quinn joins forces with a singer, an assassin and a police detective to help a young girl who had a hit placed on her after she stole a rare diamond from a crime lord.","genre_ids":[28,80],"media_type":"movie","popularity":6.6041,"vote_count":10690,"poster_path":"/h4VB6m0RwcicVEZvzftYZyKXs6K.jpg","release_date":"2020-02-05","vote_average":6.885,"backdrop_path":"/uozb2VeD87YmhoUP1RrGWfzuCrr.jpg","original_title":"Birds of Prey (and the Fantabulous Emancipation of One Harley Quinn)","original_language":"en"},{"id":398818,"adult":false,"title":"Call Me by Your Name","video":false,"overview":"In the summer of 1983, a 17-year-old Elio spends his days in his family's villa in Italy. One day Oliver, a graduate student, arrives to assist Elio's father, a professor of Greco-Roman culture. Soon, Elio and Oliver discover a summer that will alter their lives forever.","genre_ids":[10749,18],"media_type":"movie","popularity":9.3674,"vote_count":12600,"poster_path":"/mZ4gBdfkhP9tvLH1DO4m4HYtiyi.jpg","release_date":"2017-10-01","vote_a